sentences.cleaned: 习近平在贺电中指出，中葡友谊源远流长。
sentences.translation: In his congratulatory message, Xi pointed out that China-Portugal friendship has a long history.

sentences.cleaned: 建交40年来，双方秉持相互尊重、平等相待、互利共赢的精神推动双边关系健康稳定发展。
sentences.translation: Since the establishment of diplomatic ties 40 years ago, the two sides have promoted the healthy and stable development of bilateral relations in the spirit of mutual respect, equal treatment and mutual benefit and win-win results.

sentences.cleaned: 1999年，双方妥善解决澳门问题，树立了国与国通过友好协商解决历史遗留问题的典范。
sentences.translation: In 1999, the two sides properly resolved the Macao issue, setting an example for countries to resolve historical issues through friendly consultations.

sentences.cleaned: 2005年中葡建立全面战略伙伴关系以来，双方高层互访频繁，政治互信不断加深，各领域互利合作成果显著。
sentences.translation: Since the establishment of the comprehensive strategic partnership between China and Portugal in 2005, high-level visits between the two sides have been frequent, political mutual trust has deepened and mutually beneficial cooperation in various fields has yielded remarkable results.

sentences.cleaned: 不久前，我成功访问贵国，同你进行深入友好交流，共同规划了中葡关系发展新的蓝图。
sentences.translation: Not long ago, I made a successful visit to your country to have in-depth friendly exchanges with you and jointly plan a new blueprint for the development of Sino-Portuguese relations.

sentences.cleaned: 我高度重视中葡关系发展，愿同你一道努力，以两国建交40周年为新起点，推动中葡全面战略伙伴关系迈上新台阶，更好造福两国和两国人民。
sentences.translation: I attach great importance to the development of Sino-Portuguese relations and am ready to work with you to take the 40th anniversary of the establishment of diplomatic relations between the two countries as a new starting point to push the comprehensive strategic partnership between China and Portugal to a new level and better benefit the two countries and their peoples.
